#Transmissometer #1005DR was calibrated in March 2008 and drifted significantly but steadily until July 2009.

#Transmissivity data from this cruise were corrected by multiplying the original values by correction factor 2.26 which was based on the assumption that deep offshore transmissivity should be about 62% / m.
